{"tid":585171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛池灣九巴相撞癱瘓東九龍交通   消息指車長為工賊會九巴分會副主任","createTime":"2018-03-08T12:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T12:11:41.000Z","uid":20058,"like":170,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"3dc008be760ae1f1c0c9fefe4bae36fc02cabab9","tid":585171,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/08/200315_786df019d5c5578f5be62055ab09b9ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2F200315_786df019d5c5578f5be62055ab09b9ed.png&h=34ea8a69&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/thread-1059429-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkitalk.net%2FHKiTalk2%2Fthread-1059429-1-1.html&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bf6ef50e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/thread-1059429-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傍晚六點幾，清水灣道牛池灣街市外，有一部3M九巴 (LR5088) 和的士相撞，導致東九龍一帶交通嚴重擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指巴士車長報稱受傷送院，而涉事車長為曾經公開不點名批評葉蔚琳車長「白痴」的工聯會汽車交通運輸業總工會九巴分會副主任黎兆聰車長。<br />\n<br />\n祝願黎車長早日康復！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/thread-1059429-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkitalk.net%2FHKiTalk2%2Fthread-1059429-1-1.html&d=DbnstQSggiOfRAl7VhsQoHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bf6ef50e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/thread-1059429-1-1.html</a><br />\n<br />\n相片轉載自 Whatsapp group<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b86dd43b8fb96eec848dee690c09471c567e168","tid":585171,"uid":24044,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50